{
  "abstract": "The stories contained in this document are an elaboration of\r\nthe impact of the three years’ work of this project. This work\r\nhas been made possible by the financial support of USAIDKEA and collaboration of many partners who have worked\r\nclosely with ICRISAT and the staff of County Governments\r\nto interact with the famers, traders and all stakeholders\r\nin the whole value chain development process to achieve\r\nthese impacts.",
